8... O-O 9. Be2 Nc6 10. d5 { This is very weakening for White. } 10... Na5
{ White cannot play  11.b3  here as our bishop on g7 is targeting the c3-knight. }
11. Nd2 Bd7
{ And White is already in big trouble as c4 can't easily be defended. } *

