{ Black has an extra knight that will quickly come back into the game via c4, harassing the e3-bishop. White has some issues with the a1-rook. Even after something like  18.g4  Bd7  19.Rc1  Qf6  20.Be2  White has temporarily prevented ...Nc4, but  20...axb6  followed by ...Rfc8 will renew the threat. }
