16. Nd4 Nxd5 17. Nxd5 Qxd5 18. Nxf5 Qxf5 19. Rb1 Rab8
{ White has excellent compensation for the pawn, but not to the extent that Black has problems here. We can reroute our knight to d4, occupy the d-file with our f8-rook and try to create counterplay. }
*

[Event "?"]
