11. d5
{ It makes sense to kick our knight back, yet Black gets nice play in return. }
11... Ne7 12. O-O-O Nf5
{ Grabbing the White dark-square bishop is always good. Our bishop on g7 will be a major defender after that and perhaps in the long run also a great attacker. }
