9... Nc6
{ Since White's hasn't developed much the kingside yet, we don't have to be afraid of  10.d5  .   9...Bg4?!  10.Be2  Nc6  11.d5!  and we transpose toa line we wanted to avoid in Chapter 1.6.   I offer  9...d5!?  as analternative. }
10. Be2 d5 { This transposes to10.Rc1 in Chapter 1.6. } *

