{ 11.g4?!  Bd7  . As in the main line, the question remains whether this inclusion benefits White or Black. }
11... cxd5 12. cxd5 Na6
{ Notice we cannot play  12...N8d7  because of  13.g4  trapping the bishop on f5. }
13. g4
{ 13.O-O?  dxe5  14.fxe5  Nb4  with problems for White as we are threatening both ...Nc2 and ...Nxd5.   13.Qd2?  Nb4  14.O-O  dxe5  and White loses the d5-pawn.   However,  13.Qd4!  protects everything, including a ...Nb4 jump. I think White is much better here and that is why I'm going for  @@StartFEN@@rn1qk2r/ppp1ppbp/1n1pb1p1/3PP3/2P2P2/2N1B3/PP4PP/R2QKBNR b KQkq - 0 8@@EndFEN@@  8...Bc8  asmy recommendation. }
