6. Nf3 e6 7. c4
{ This is too weakening. The principled  7.Bd3  intending to trade bishops is coverednext. }
7... Nb4 8. Qxd8+ Kxd8 9. Na3 Bc5
{ The bishop is very well placed on c5, where it especially hinders White's O-O and Be3. Black has a much easier development. }
*

