{ The only way to disrupt our position. We have to deal with g7. } 13... Qd7
{ Yet we can give it quite happily!  13...O-O?  14.Bh6  and White wins the exchange. }
14. Be3
{ 14.Qxg7?  O-O-O  and our pressure over the g-file is going to be immense. }
14... h5
