12. Bd2 Bxd2+
{ This has fewer games in the database than  12...Qa5  , yet I think it is a bit easier to equalise completely. After  13.a3  Bxd2+  14.Qxd2  Qxd2+  15.Kxd2  Bg4  16.Rhe1  perhaps White can claim a very slight advantage in this ending due to the isolated black pawn. }
