{ Played a few times by legendary player Evgeny Sveshnikov. White is threatening Bg5. }
8... bxc5 { We accept the challenge. } 9. Bg5 Be7 10. Bxe7 Qxe7 11. Qxg7 Rf8
12. Nf3
{ White continues with their development and will get an edge if they manage to complete it. }
12... cxd4 13. cxd4 Qb4+ { A devastating check. } *

