12. Bd2 O-O 13. Qb3
{ 13.a3  Nxc3  14.bxc3  Nc6∓  is also wonderful for Black, with the same ideas to put pressure on the a3-pawn. }
13... Nxc3 14. bxc3 Nc6 { And Black's position has much more potential. } *

