11... a5 { Just grabbing space on the queenside. } 12. Ne4
{ 12.a4  b4  intending ...c5.   12.c4?!  bxc4  13.Nxc4  c5!  Black has equalised. We can develop our bishop to b7 and enjoy a pleasant position. }
12... a4 13. h3 { If White play slow, we can break in the centre: } 13... e5
