e5
{ We want to target the centre quickly. And now is the right time - the bishop is slightly misplaced on  b3  at the moment.  11...Nf6?!  is Kasparov,G @@StartBracket@@2795@@EndBracket@@-Adams,M @@StartBracket@@2665@@EndBracket@@ Linares 1997. }
