{ 15.Bc2?!  allows us to exchange White's active pieces with  15...N7e6  16.Nxe6  Qxd1  17.Rxd1  Bxe6  18.Nd2  Rad8  and now Black is the one with activity. }
15... Rf7 { White has to be very careful here. } *

